[{"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-04T22:15:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/GYyoK9-WUAArkoo.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Each week on Polygon, we round up the most notable new releases to streaming and VOD, highlighting the biggest and best new movies for you to watch at home.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Evil is in question this week, as Ryusuke Hamaguchi\u2019s <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/reviews/24153139/evil-does-not-exist-review-ryusuke-hamaguchi\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.polygon.com/reviews/24153139/evil-does-not-exist-review-ryusuke-hamaguchi\">Evil Does Not Exist</a></em> and James Watkins\u2019 2024 remake of <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/movies/452170/sad-endings-remake-speak-no-evil\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.polygon.com/movies/452170/sa", "id": 1269588, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/entertainment/456330/new-movies-deadpool-wolverine-netflix-platform-2-speak-no-evil-watch-streaming", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Deadpool &#038; Wolverine, Speak No Evil, Netflix\u2019s The Platform 2, and every movie new to streaming this week", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-04T21:35:19+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/09/Zelda-Echoes-of-Wisdom-smoothies.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Before I soapbox about smoothies and women, I must make one thing clear: The girls are not all right. And by \u201cthe girls\u201d I mean myself, and a few of my other friends who don\u2019t identify as men. When I heard that <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/the-legend-of-zelda-echoes-of-wisdom/40934\">The Legend of Zelda: Echoes of Wisdom</a></em> would finally put Zelda in the driver\u2019s seat of her own game, I was obviously ecstatic. I am a woman, and I like to play games as a woman when possible \u2014 and this is my first chance to do so for my all-time favorite franchise.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">But now that the game is out, I\u2019m <em>all</em> in ", "id": 1269044, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/opinion/461122/zelda-echoes-of-wisdom-smoothies-diet-culture", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "I\u2019m offended that the only thing Zelda can consume in Echoes of Wisdom is smoothies", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-04T19:57:53+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"Zelda holds a golden egg from a chest in Echoes of Wisdom\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Grezzo, Nintendo EPD/Nintendo via Polygon\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/2023010120393300_s.jpg?qual