cation-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/05/jlee_241004_1001_pogo_masterball.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>Years after the game first arrived, a <strong>Master Ball</strong> can be obtained in <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/pokemon-go/38713\">Pok\u00e9mon Go</a>.</em></p>\n\n<p>The Master Ball is perhaps the most iconic Pok\u00e9mon-catching device of all time. First appearing way back in <em>Pok\u00e9mon Red</em> and <em>Blue</em> of the main series, the Master Ball has a very special trait \u2014 a 100% catch rate on any Pok\u00e9mon you use it on.</p>\n\n<p>Long-time players of <em>Pok\u00e9mon Go</em> will be very familiar with that sinking feeling of finishing a raid and failing to catch the subsequent encounter, and with the Master Ball, this is one way to ensure the Pok\u00e9mon will defin", "id": 1267835, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/pokemon-go-guide/23732462/master-ball-research-unlock-use-miss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "How to get a Master Ball in Pok\u00e9mon Go, and when is it best to use one?", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-04T16:18:58+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Niantic / The Pok\u00e9mon Company\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25105384/pokemon_go_master_ball_special_research.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/pokemon-go/38713\"><em>Pok\u00e9mon Go</em></a> has presented players with yet another opportunity to grab a <strong>Master Ball</strong>, if they want it. For $7.99, players can nab a pass in the shop that rewards a load of XP and a Master Ball.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">While the steps for this paid research seem daunting, you have an unlimited amount of time to do it, so it shouldn\u2019t be that bad. We list out the steps and whether or not it may be worth buying below. At the bottom of this page, we also list the older Master Ball research from November 2023, ", "id": 1267836, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/pokemon-go-guide/23972442/master-ball-special-research-quest-steps-worth-buying", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Pok\u00e9mon Go Master Ball Special Research quest steps, and is it worth buying?", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-04T16:04:25+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/unnamed_a4bcd6.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/pokemon-go-guide\"><em>Pok\u00e9mon Go</em></a> is hosting a \u201c<strong>Galarian Expedition</strong>\u201d event from<strong> Oct. 4-11</strong>, permanently bringing some new shiny Legendary Pok\u00e9mon into the game via Daily Adventure Incense, alongside other event bonuses.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-